          <span class="bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">‚úì Case Studies</span>
          <span class="bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">‚úì Analytics Tools</span>
